plot: Johnny has recently returned to Los Angeles from an adventure up in Canada. A journey that has been an emotional roller-coaster ride - fun filled, entertaining, action packed, wildly adventurous, suspenseful, informative, challenging, thrilling but yet potentially fatal and sad to numerous degrees.
